## Swap status

> In Progress Response

```json
{
  "status": {
    "type": "in-progress"
  }
}
```

> Hold Response

```json
{
  "status": {
    "type": "hold"
  }
}
```

> Completed Response

```json
{
  "status": {
    "type": "completed"
  }
}
```

A swap `status.type` indicates the current state of a request to swap a payment method with a particular company.

### in-progress

The swap of the payment method is currently in progress.

### hold

The swap of the payment method is currently on hold as described in the [Auth Status](#auth-status).

### completed

The swap of the payment method has been completed successfully.
